text: Jens Niehls (born 1 January 1951) is a German equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:German male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of East Germany Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Halle (Saale)
